he.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df7f7f0141302f4e19c3d6b51e260e1b47044d7","tid":1082240,"uid":52358,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:03:17.000Z","msg":"終於唔駛去日本城當去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d4dee814489bc3e70736a343b93413b3111b8d","tid":1082240,"uid":138479,"like":159,"dislike":1,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:04:00.000Z","msg":"19呢個idea其他人有sell過比777<br />\n但經過微調後，決定改為「明日大連」"},{"pid":"20695d20e9fd50f3f94cc7f93b07733a2195c741","tid":1082240,"uid":87339,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:04:41.000Z","msg":"再嘈就明日大灣"},{"pid":"0051cb2c9f1e04812ab5339df4cc4ac0ae76b682","tid":1082240,"uid":202198,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:06:20.000Z","msg":"條go鐵支線可以升格做日本新幹線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d15cdab0c402c2fbd4b72222be7a698e3a7dc1","tid":1082240,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:06:40.000Z","msg":"要開十間驚安先似"},{"pid":"3485ddadfca46bd37366a58c477f34badbf07bb7","tid":1082240,"uid":8377,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"37d15cdab0c402c2fbd4b72222be7a698e3a7dc1","tid":1082240,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:06:40.000Z","msg":"要開十間驚安先似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:08:27.000Z","msg":"好似已經黎港開分店了"},{"pid":"4eedd1ba5cf173ad1b12c8d4bbbb6006054d6d3f","tid":1082240,"uid":134215,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:10:44.000Z","msg":"相對濕度: 0%"},{"pid":"4c8f888a4219729b11355b03c1aad7c435d6cfa5","tid":1082240,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:14:30.000Z","msg":"直線抽擊"},{"pid":"3212cf7b0686332c05eb0e0dabe7d466d0f4f8a4","tid":1082240,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":60,"score":-59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-0